<li>Content briefs are created with SEO requirements</li>
<li>Articles are written and optimized</li>
<li>Content is pushed to the headless CMS via API</li>
<li>Frontend rebuilds or regenerates affected pages</li>
<li>Sitemap updates automatically</li>
<li>New content is live and indexable within minutes</li>
</ol>
